            "title": "翰森製藥去年純利增長27.1% 擬派末期息增至每股20港仙",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">韓森製藥(03692)公布，於2025年度溢利55.55億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升27.1%；擬派末期息增至每股20港仙。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：翰森製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source-web_03692-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：翰森製藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source-web_03692-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：翰森製藥官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入已派中期息，該公司全年每股共派43.16港仙，較2024年度的33.63港仙提升28.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內該公司收入150.28億元，按年升22.6%；創新藥與合作產品銷售收入約123.54億元，增長30.4%，佔總收入比例升至82.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">去年研發開支約33.58億元，按年增24.3%，佔收入比例約22.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810344-%e7%bf%b0%e6%a3%ae%e8%a3%bd%e8%97%a5%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b727-1-%e6%93%ac%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e%e8%87%b3%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a120%e6%b8%af%e4%bb%99",
